# Firebase server-side credentials (Admin SDK service-account keys) — never commit
*-firebase-adminsdk-*.json
# Client configs are package/bundle-ID-restricted and safe to commit (like iOS):
# GoogleService-Info.plist (iOS) and google-services.json (Android) are tracked so
# EAS managed builds can copy them. See docs/firebase-android-setup.md.
